1. *Pritiskom* na dugme otvara se vrata. (By pressing the button, the door opens.)
2. Temperatura se može regulisati *pritiskom* na dugme. (The temperature can be regulated by pressing a button.)
3. Osećajte se sigurno *pritiskom* na taster za alarm. (Feel safe by pressing the alarm button.)
4. *Pritiskom* na kočnicu zaustavili smo automobil. (We stopped the car by pressing the brake.)
5. Oslobodite se stresa *pritiskom* na određene tačke na telu. (Release stress by applying pressure to specific points on the body.)
6. *Pritiskom* na dugme uključite svetlo. (Turn on the light by pressing the button.)
7. Neka vam bude lakše *pritiskom* na dugme za lift. (Make it easier for yourself by pressing the elevator button.)
8. Uspešno smo izvršili plaćanje *pritiskom* na dugme "Potvrdi". (We successfully made the payment by pressing the "Confirm" button.)
9. Smanjite rizik od nezgoda *pritiskom* na kočnicu. (Reduce the risk of accidents by pressing the brake.)
10. *Pritiskom* na tipku otvara se program. (The program opens by pressing the button.)